{% block body %}

 <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">

        <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li><a href="#">Accueil</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Annonces</a></li>
            <li class="active">Chercher une annonce</li>
            <li class="active">Villa avec piscine</li>
        </ol>


        <div class="title-details"><span>{{annonce.titre}}</span><span>{{annonce.prix}} Euro</span></div>

    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">
        <div class=" wells list-options nmrg">
            <ul>
                <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i>Envoyer Par E-Mail</a></li>
                <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-phone"></i>Afficher le numéro</a></li>
                <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>Créer une alerte</a></li>
                <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-thumbs-o-up"></i>Ajouter à mes favoris</a></li>
                <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-print"></i>Imprimer</a></li>
                <li><a href=""><i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-left"></i>Retour aux Annonces</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9">
        <div id="owl-galerie" class="owl-carousel owl-theme">

            <div class="item"><img src="{{asset('bundles/coachannonce/images/uploads/')}}{{annonce.path}}" alt="The Last of us"></div>
            

        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h4 class="br-title">Description</h4>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-2">
                <img src="img/biens/maison-3.png" class="img-responsive" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-10">

                <p>There are many variations of passages of Lorem Ipsum available, but the majority have suffered alteration in some form, by injected humour, or randomised words which don't look even slightly believable. If you are going to use a passage of Lorem Ipsum, you need to be sure there isn't anything embarrassing hidden in the middle of text. </p>
